title: Finieous Fingers 2
description:
The Finieous Fingers cartoon from The Dragon #38 to The Dragon #54.  This is from the end of the comics covered in the Finieous Fingers Treasury to the end of FF in The Dragon.

After this FF was briefly in The Space Gamer, Adventure Gaming, The Fantasy Gamer, and (by a different author) Shadis.  However, I do not have any of those strips.  Anyone out there got 'em?
